      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANJO STATUE (4) is a first starter from the John Grief kennel by Flying Stanley out of Miss Springfield. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Strong market watch advised but profiles nicely for this. BARRELLED (1) finished well back on debut when sixth (24.13) at Shepparton over 390m. Drops down the inside box this time. Can feature with the right run. GO FORWARD TIGER (7) still a maiden but rarely out of the finish recording six placings from eight starts. Hit the frame again last start finishing second (23.38) at Richmond. Will give a great sight again. BAD BOY BANJO (2) makes debut for the James Goddard kennel. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
